jde.parser.visitor
Class DepthFirstVisitor

java.lang.Object
  jde.parser.visitor.DepthFirstVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Visitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
GetVariables, GetVariablesVisitor, TreeDumper, TreeFormatter
public class DepthFirstVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor

Provides default methods which visit each node in the tree in depth-first order. Your visitors may extend this class.
